sub_title: MSc Neuroscience student at Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam
summary: I'm currently a second-year neuroscience research master's student at Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam, with a specific emphasis on clinical research. My undergraduate studies in psychology instilled in me a deep passion for research, motivating me to pursue a career in academia. My particular research interests center around clinical neuroscience and neuroimaging to comprehend the fundamental neural processes that underlie different neuropsychiatric and neurodegenerative disorders.
